item.description:
Join us for a night of music and fun with She's Busy at Point Breeze. The whole She's Busy band will be there performing from 8:00 p.m. to midnight.

We are reserving a table near the band and dance floor and hope you can join us. If you plan on having dinner, please arrive early......table will be reserved for 7:00 p.m. Those coming for dinner will be responsible for their own food and beverages. Those wishing to come for the band only, can arrive anytime.  Please state in your RSVP whether you will be joining us for dinner or not.

Bring a canned good or two and the cover charge is waived.

If you have any questions, please post them or email us.

For more information on She's Busy go to link below:

http://shesbusy.com/

 

www.pointbreezeonwebsterlake.com
item.how_to_find_us: Ask when you come in, we should be on the porch by the band.
item.why: the band is great....and you'll have a great time!
item.name: She's Busy at Point Breeze, Webster, MA
